---
title: Moroccan Steak with Quick-Pickled Lemon and Couscous
description: We're so excited for this delicious steak dinner! Served with a veggie packed couscous side dish, it'll be like taking a trip to Morocco without ever leaving your home.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/moroccan-steak-da2b5056.jpg
